product_description.Punch-hole Display: Get set to view all visuals clearly and play your favourite games vividly on this smartphone’s 90 Hz Punch-hole display.
product_description.3D Iridescent Wave Design: This phone will be worth flaunting around, thanks to its attractive 3D iridescent wave design.
product_description.Integrated Curved Body: Even though this phone is backed by a powerful 5000 mAh battery, its lightweight and ultra-thin design will ensure that it fits into a single hand. It also boasts a body ratio of 20:9.
product_description.High-capacity Battery: You can continue using the phone for a long time, as it comes with a high-capacity 5000 mAh battery that supports 18 W fast charging.
product_description.Super Power Saving Mode: Phone low on charge? The Super Power Saving mode will ensure that you continue to stay on the grid. Oh, and that’s not all! The Sleep Standby Optimization will help prolong the power as well.
product_description.Qualcomm Snapdragon Processor: No unnecessary lag or waiting anymore! This smartphone’s powerful octa-core processor will facilitate great performance.
product_description.Reduced Lag Time: This smartphone’s RAM + optimization will make sure that there’s no lag when you open or run an application you want to use. This way, you can be assured to have a seamless mobile experience.
product_description.Dual Stereo Speakers: Featuring dual stereo speakers, this smartphone will leave you enthralled with powerful and enthralling audio. It also features Dirac’s automatic audio optimization so all you have to do is sit back and enjoy your favourite tunes.
product_description.Camera Features: This smartphone is all you need for capturing memories vividly and clearly, thanks to its triple rear camera system (13 MP main camera + 2 MP depth camera + 2 MP macro lens). It also features an 8 MP selfie camera.
product_description.Dazzle Color Mode: Want to retain the vibrancy of the picture? The Dazzle Color mode will restore the pictures to their dynamic colors so that they continue to remain vibrant memories in your gallery.
product_description.Portrait Mode: Capture picture-perfect shots of your loved ones using this camera’s portrait mode with natural bokeh effect.
product_description.Filter Lenses: Quirk-up your pictures with the help of this smartphone’s collection of filters.
product_description.Capture Every Detail: With 4 cm close-up shots, you can capture every detail in the best manner. Oh, and this smartphone’s AI beautification will facilitate customised retouches to enhance your picture.
product_description.ColorOS: With the ColorOS in place, this smartphone will pave the way for a seamless experience with features such as Multi-user and Icon Pull-down Gesture.
